tags.description: Elevator from ground level (Riverside Park or parking lot) to top level (fourth Riverbank State Park).  The 2nd and 3rd levels are for the North River Wastewater Resource Recovery Facility for which this is not an entrance.
The incline is very steep. This is a ramp from 11th Ave to the upper portion of Riverside Park.
The northern end of Hamilton Place is painted green to signify the area is open to pedestrians and bicyclist only.
